<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lovat leh hal zawh nungin!
 Chi pha chuh I tuh ui;
 Mahleh Pathien khut hat chun,
 Tui buokin a khansak;
 Phalbi'n vuk a kieksak a,
 Lumna'n a hihkhang a;
 Huihchim, nivak A piei,
 Hinna dingin guoh tui tawh.

[V2]
 Thilpha I neih cheng cheng,
 Chunglam apat ahi;
 Ei hehpihna ziekin Lalpa,
 Chuh pakcha tiu.

[V3]
 2. Nai leh gamla a thil cheng,
 Siempa Amah ahi;
 Pakcha hawihna A pie a,
 Aksi vakna a piei;
 Huih leh tuiin A thu awi,
 Vacha haw le A vak;
 Ei uh A chate vang hi,
 Nicheng an ei pien a.

[V4]
 3. Na thilsiem haw cheng ziek hin,
 Lalpa, ka hun pakchau;
 Buhtuh phat leh buh-at phat,
 Damna nei piek ziek hin;
 Nei hehpihna zieka thil,
 Ka hun piekuh pawmin;
 Na thil deihpen ka lunguh,
 Na kawmah ka hun pieu.</lyrics>
<title>WE PLOUGH THE FIELDS</title>
<hymn_number>420</hymn_number>
</song>